*Harold Lever (7 January 1967 – 29 August 1967) 
*Peter Shore (7 January 1967 – 29 August 1967) 
*Alan Williams (29 August 1967 – 6 October 1969) 
*Edmund Dell (29 August 1967 – 6 April 1968)

